		{
			"name": "reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xweFgwSnRPRWxLYjFkQlluVktkVlIzVHpoVGRVRRAB",
			"relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 часа назад",
			"rating": 1,
			"text": {
				"text": "I booked a consultation to find out the cost of removing a pigmentation spot. At no point during the booking process was I informed that the consultation would be paid. In the end , I was charged 50€ , which feels quite expensive for what was essentially a brief verbal recommendation (I was simply advised to use a cream instead of undergoing any procedure).\n\nIt would be much more fair and transparent to clearly inform clients in advance about consultation fees , especially when the visit is only meant to determine the price of a potential treatment.",
				"languageCode": "en"
			},
			"originalText": {
				"text": "I booked a consultation to find out the cost of removing a pigmentation spot. At no point during the booking process was I informed that the consultation would be paid. In the end , I was charged 50€ , which feels quite expensive for what was essentially a brief verbal recommendation (I was simply advised to use a cream instead of undergoing any procedure).\n\nIt would be much more fair and transparent to clearly inform clients in advance about consultation fees , especially when the visit is only meant to determine the price of a potential treatment.",
				"languageCode": "en"
			},
